            "electoral_victory_message": "''",
            "electoral_loss_message": "''",
            "no_electoral_majority_message": "''",
            "description_as_running_mate": "<i>This may sound trite, but I believe it to be true: Entrepreneurship is the fabric of what America is all about.</i><p>Vivek Ramaswamy is a rising star in the MAGA movement. He is an entrepreneur just like you, founding Roivant Sciences in 2014 and is a child of immigrants from India. He did run in the 2024 Republican primaries, mostly standing up against the \"identity crisis\" when it comes to climate change, gender ideology, and COVID-19. He just embodies the anti-establishment movement that has been going on since Donald Trump entered the political world in 2015. He puts America First, he has been a strong critic of the Schwarzenegger administration on social issues and COVID mandates, and is a multimillionaire tech guru that can help you double down on appealing to upper-class businessmen and tech gurus across the country.</p>",
